# NOTE:
# Generated pipeline artifacts (extracted_content.json, entities.json,
# entity_sentiment.json, qa_report.json, cost_report.json, run_metrics.json,
# sentiment_timeline.json, llm_calls.jsonl, reports/, Artifacts/) are
